{% extends "base.html.j2" %}

{% block title %}
<title>Dry Rock - About</title>
{% endblock title %}

{% block content %}
<div class="row mb-5">
  <div class="col">
    <section id="about" class="section-header">
      <h1 class="display-4 text-center pb-1">About</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Ever found yourself clicking through forecast after forecast trying to figure out where
        to go climbing at the weekend? Well then you've come to the right place!
      </p>
    </section>
    <hr class="my-4 mx-4">
    <section id="instructions" class="mb-4">
      <p>
        Dry Rock is designed to be a one stop shop for figuring out where to go climbing.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          Select your location from the list on the top left, and select your preferred units from the dropdown on the
          top
          right.
        </li>
        <li>
          The overview table for each area has a 7-day rainfall summary for popular climbing destinations in that
          area.
        </li>
        <li>
          Low rainfall values are shown in <span class="text-success">green</span> to make them easier to spot.
        </li>
        <li>
          Clicking a row in the overview table will take you to a 7-day forecast for that place.
        </li>
        <li>
          Clicking a row in the 7-day forecast table will show you a pop up with an hourly (or 6-hourly) detailed
          forecast
          for that day.
        </li>
        <li>
          Clicking the overview button will take you back to the overview table.
        </li>
        <li>
          Bookmark the page relevant to you to make it easy to find.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section id="app" class="mb-4">
      <h2>Is there an app?</h2>
      <p>
        There is not an app but if you go to the page relevant to you on your mobile web browser, hit the three dots on
        the top bar and select "save to home screen" a link to the site will appear on your home screen. And of course
        you
        can bookmark the page to make it easier to find ðŸ˜‰
      </p>
    </section>
    <section id="info">
      <h2>More Info</h2>
      <p>
        Forecast data is provided by the <a href="https://www.met.no/en"> Norwegian Meteorological Institute</a>. Many
        thanks to them for making their data freely available.
      </p>
      <p>
        This is an open source project, the source code is available on <a
          href="https://github.com/Rory-Sullivan/Dry-Rock">GitHub</a>. You can get in touch with me there or just say
        'hi'
        at the local crag!
      </p>

      <div class="row align-items-center justify-content-around">
        <div class="col-auto text-center">
          <a href="https://github.com/Rory-Sullivan/Dry-Rock"><img src="/static/logos/GitHub-Mark/GitHub-Mark-64px.png"
              alt="GitHub logo"></a>
        </div>
        <div class="col-auto text-center">
          <a href="https://www.met.no/en"><img src="/static/logos/NMI-Logo/Met_RGB_Horisontal_ENG.jpg"
              alt="Norwegian Meteorological Institute logo" height="120px"></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>
{% endblock content %}
